{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.wsj.com/articles/behind-the-long-painful-birth-of-the-worlds-biggest-tech-fund-1495214782"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 He launched the Vision Fund in 2017}}, with funds from SoftBank and investors such as Saudi Arabia's Public Investment Fund. The fund has its own investment committee, including Mr. Son, that approves deals. Some of its biggest deals are also brought before SoftBank's board.\
